commits.author: Dongjoo Seo
commits.message:
[Test] Require PYTHONHASHSEED for lookup client tests (#2392)

* [Test] Require PYTHONHASHSEED for lookup client tests

Add PYTHONHASHSEED requirement to test_lmcache_lookup_client.py to
reflect production environment where LMCacheLookupClient and
LMCacheLookupServer run in separate processes (scheduler vs worker).

In production, consistent hashing across processes requires
PYTHONHASHSEED to be set. Tests now skip if PYTHONHASHSEED is not set,
with a clear message explaining the requirement.

Run with: PYTHONHASHSEED=0 pytest tests/v1/lookup_client/test_lmcache_lookup_client.py

Signed-off-by: Dongjoo Seo <dongjoo.seo1@samsung.com>
Signed-off-by: DongDongJu <commisori28@gmail.com>

* fix style

Signed-off-by: Dongjoo Seo <dongjoo.seo1@samsung.com>

Signed-off-by: Dongjoo Seo <dongjoo.seo1@samsung.com>

commits.author: Dongjoo Seo
commits.message:
[Test] Require PYTHONHASHSEED for lookup client tests (#2392)

* [Test] Require PYTHONHASHSEED for lookup client tests

Add PYTHONHASHSEED requirement to test_lmcache_lookup_client.py to
reflect production environment where LMCacheLookupClient and
LMCacheLookupServer run in separate processes (scheduler vs worker).

In production, consistent hashing across processes requires
PYTHONHASHSEED to be set. Tests now skip if PYTHONHASHSEED is not set,
with a clear message explaining the requirement.

Run with: PYTHONHASHSEED=0 pytest tests/v1/lookup_client/test_lmcache_lookup_client.py

Signed-off-by: Dongjoo Seo <dongjoo.seo1@samsung.com>
